tags: Geo News|Mushtail Afraad|Wazir-e-Ittelaat|Fayyaz ul Hassan Chohan|Tashaddud|lawyer|Breaking News|cardiology hospital|Punjab|police officials|enforcement personnel|police vehicle on fire|public property|several videos
description: Mushtail Afraad Ka Wazir-e-Ittelaat Fayyaz ul Hassan Chohan Par TashaddudLAHORE: A group of lawyers on Wednesday stormed the emergency ward of Punjab Institute of Cardiology in Lahore, vandalised public property, set a police vehicle on fire and attacked provincial minister Fayazul Hasan Chauhan, Geo News reported. According to several videos of the incident shared on Twitter, police officials, clad in riot gear, were rendered helpless as a swarm of lawyers, outnumbering the law enforcement personnel, broke the entrance of the hospital. There were reports of casualties at the emergency ward of the hospital as a result of the confusion and fear that spread inside the facility as the lawyers barged into the building. It was not clear why the group of lawyers stormed the cardiology hospital.
